{"tid":1145724,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple售後服務再次屌打三星","createTime":"2019-05-08T22:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T09:09:28.000Z","uid":109383,"like":35,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"465b8ff6b832046eb2452be65f95e580b13c7095","tid":1145724,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T22:16:24.000Z","msg":"Apple內部通告指示 Apple Watch Series 2 維修可更換 Series 3<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當 Apple 某些舊型號產品的零件短缺時，顧客將損壞產品拿去維修，往往會獲得免費更換至較新的型號。類似的情況最近發生在 Apple Watch Series 2 之上，外界傳媒最近報導指，Apple Store 和授權服務供應商都收到 Apple 的指示，為損壞 38mm 鋁合金外殼的 Apple Watch Series 2 客戶更換成 Series 3 型號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=805520\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F%3Fattachment_id%3D805520&h=6add9e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指該內部文件還提到，假如顧客不滿意由 Series 2 更換成 Series 3 的安排，Apple 甚至可以為他們辦理退款手續。不少網民對於 Apple 讓已使用而且壞掉的產品退款，感到不可思議，認為這樣的服務很好。提供退款安排可能是因為 Apple Watch Series 3 需要兼容 watchOS 4 或較新系統版本的 iPhone，即是更換手錶後，iPhone 5 或 iPhone 5C 的手機用戶將無法正常使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失戀狗肯收皮未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ca8a5af7ce9b36509563327efaba4b32f586fd","tid":1145724,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"包括香港？"},{"pid":"4281a54d69b2c8d8294ae194b341ed0157ec65bc","tid":1145724,"uid":43178,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"f3ca8a5af7ce9b36509563327efaba4b32f586fd","tid":1145724,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"包括香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T02:10:45.000Z","ms